---

<section class="testimonials">
  <div class="container">

    <p class="testimonials__eyebrow">Student Reviews</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">What Our Students Say</h2>
    <hr class="gold-line" />
    <p class="section-subtitle">Join thousands of students who have achieved academic success with ThesisArcPro.</p>

    <div class="testimonials__grid">

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
