          <div class="author__info">
            <span class="author__name">Sarah M.</span>
            <span class="author__title">PhD Student, University of London</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card testimonial-card--featured">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__text">"I was struggling with my research paper and had only 3 days left. ThesisArcPro delivered a perfectly written, well-researched paper on time. My professor was impressed with the quality!"</p>
