          <div class="author__info">
            <span class="author__name">James K.</span>
            <span class="author__title">Masters Student, University of Nairobi</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__text">"As a high school student, I was worried about finding reliable help with my essays. ThesisArcPro was professional, fast, and the quality was outstanding. My grades have improved significantly!"</p>
        <div class="testimonial-card__author">
          <div class="author__avatar">AT</div>
          <div class="author__info">
            <span class="author__name">Amina T.</span>
            <span class="author__title">High School Student, Nairobi</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__text">"The editing and proofreading service transformed my thesis. The expert not only corrected my grammar but also improved the overall flow and academic tone. Highly recommended!"</p>
        <div class="testimonial-card__author">
          <div class="author__avatar">RO</div>
          <div class="author__info">
            <span class="author__name">Robert O.</span>
            <span class="author__title">Masters Student, Strathmore University</span>
          </div>
