      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__text">"I needed help with my research methodology and statistical analysis. The consultant was extremely patient and explained everything clearly. My research is now solid and well-structured."</p>
        <div class="testimonial-card__author">
          <div class="author__avatar">FN</div>
          <div class="author__info">
            <span class="author__name">Faith N.</span>
            <span class="author__title">PhD Researcher, Kenyatta University</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__text">"Fast, reliable and professional. I have used ThesisArcPro three times now for different assignments and the quality has been consistent every time. This is my go-to academic support service!"</p>
